@startuml sequence_gui_mode_switch

participant User
participant CalculatorWindow
participant GUISessionAdapter
participant CalculatorSession
participant ModeConfig

== User switches to Scientific mode ==

User -> CalculatorWindow : clicks "Scientific" button
activate CalculatorWindow

CalculatorWindow -> GUISessionAdapter : set_mode("scientific")
activate GUISessionAdapter

GUISessionAdapter -> CalculatorSession : set_mode("scientific")
activate CalculatorSession

CalculatorSession -> ModeConfig : get_mode_config("scientific")
activate ModeConfig
ModeConfig --> CalculatorSession : ModeConfig(SCIENTIFIC, [ops...])
deactivate ModeConfig

CalculatorSession -> CalculatorSession : _current_mode = "scientific"\n_operation_list = scientific_ops
CalculatorSession --> GUISessionAdapter : True
deactivate CalculatorSession

GUISessionAdapter --> CalculatorWindow : (returns)
deactivate GUISessionAdapter

CalculatorWindow -> CalculatorWindow : update_operation_buttons()
note right: Destroys old buttons,\ncreates new buttons\nfor scientific ops

CalculatorWindow --> User : Operation buttons refreshed
deactivate CalculatorWindow

@enduml
